intro: I tailor my lessons so that the student feels comfortable to talk to me and i am able to gain the trust of the student as to what I'm teaching them.
My teaching method is hands on and enjoyable. I treat every student as unique and focus on their strengths and weaknesses of all activities.
testimonial: Sports are about those incredible moments where sheer human will and desire overcomes the odds. These are the moments we remember.
Age is no barrier. With this teacher i pushed my limits
I always felt that my greatest asset was not my physical ability, it was my mental ability.
